title: Reference a Jenkins Agent in a Pipeline
tags: @zettel _method jenkins
roam-id: d46fbfdf-46d2-47fa-b3bf-ee357a0f2be3
type: text/markdown

- say you have an agent called \"agent-java\" then you call it like this

``` groovy
pipeline {
    agent { label 'agent-java' }

    stages {
        stage('Hello') {
            steps {
                echo 'Hello World'
            }
        }
    }
}
```
